Package lienub.dev.lienubsteam.utils.managers

Class TeamManager

java.lang.Object
lienub.dev.lienubsteam.utils.managers.TeamManager
public class TeamManager extends Object
The class Team manager. Manages all teams and their members. Handles invitations, join requests and teleport requests. Handles team creation, deletion and retrieval. Handles player retrieval and role assignment. Handles chunk retrieval and team assignment. Handles player teleportation.
Since:
1.0.0
Version:
